ian Handicap looks to offer value as the minnows look to make history by recording their first win at the Bernabeu. Read more about Asian Handicap betting here.\r\n\r\nLos Blancos should still have enough to edge it though. However with just one clean sheet in their last 6 Copa del Rey home games, the visitors could nick a goal and going for 2-1 Real Madrid looks a decent bet in the correct score market.'),
