(154, 1, '2017-12-06 05:50:15', '2017-12-06 05:50:15', '<div class="ui horizontal divider invis_clss" style="margin-top:1em;"><i class="ui white custom info icon"></i> More Info</div>\r\n<div class="fst segment blog content" id="seocontent"><h1>Free Golf Betting Tips</h1><p>Wondering who to back at the next golf tournament?</p><p>Whether you’re watching the Majors, the Ryder Cup or the PGA tour, our Golf tipsters at Free Super Tips specialise in finding you value in the golf betting market. We crunch the stats and analyse the players&nbsp;to provide you with the best golf betting tips. Our tipsters will also make sure you&nbsp;get&nbsp;the best Golf betting odds available with our predictions. This will squeeze out even more value and help you bash the bookies.</p><p>Best of all, it’s completely free. No subscriptions, no sign up fees. no memberships– none of that nonsense. Just the best golf bets.</p><h2>When Are Your Golf Tips Posted?</h2><p>Our tips for weekly PGA and European Tour events are updated by Tuesday each week. This gives our tipsters enough time to assess course information, form and analyse last weeks rounds. To make sure we get the value for the Majors – The&nbsp;Masters, US Open, The Open Championship and The U.S. PGA Championship our predictions&nbsp;are posted a week in advance.</p><h2>Predictions For All Golf Majors</h2><h3>The US Masters</h3><p>The first major championship of the year is The US Masters hosted in April from Augusta national in Georgia, USA. Check out our <a href="http://stagingonline.net/projects/freesupertips/tips/us-masters-betting-tips-predictions/">US Masters betting tips for 2017</a>.</p><h3>US Open</h3><p>The second major championship of the year is hosted from Erin Hills, Wisconsin USA. Our&nbsp;<a href="http://stagingonline.net/projects/freesupertips/tips/us-open-betting-tips-predictions/">2017 US Open betting tips</a>&nbsp;will be live early June for the tournament.</p><h3>The Open Championship</h3><p>Royal Birkdale hosts the 146th Open Championship in early September. Check out our <a href="http://stagingonline.net/projects/freesupertips/tips/british-open-championship-betting-tips-predictions/">British Open Championship betting tips for 2017</a>.</p><h3>US PGA Championship</h3><p>The final major championship of the year comes from Quail Hollow Club, North Carolina, USA.&nbsp;View our <a href="https://www.freesupertips.co.uk/tips/pga-championship-betting-tips-predictions/">2017 US PGA Championship betting tips</a> now.</p><h2>Specialist Golf Tipsters For Both Major Tours</h2><p>Our Golf tipsters provide you with weekly tips from both the European Tour and PGA tour events. For those of you who are new to Golf betting we explain quickly how both tours work.</p><h3><strong>European Tour</strong></h3><p>The European Tour takes place over 47 tournaments throughout the year. It starts in November in South Africa and concludes 12 months later with the DP World Tour Championship Dubai. Players battle it out over the season to finish top of the order of merit, now named The Race To Dubai. A bonus pool of $7.5 million is distributed among the top 15 players at the end of the season with the winner taking $1.5 million.</p><h3><strong>PGA Tour</strong></h3><p>The PGA Tour is the American version&nbsp;which starts in October and runs until the end of September with the&nbsp;FedExCup playoffs. The FedExCup is the Championship trophy for the PGA tour which is decided by four playoff events – The Barclays, Deutsche Bank Championship, BMW Championship and Tour Championship. The player with the most points at the end of the playoffs wins the cup itself and $10 million.</p><h2>The Best Golf Betting Odds</h2><p>Our golf tipsters find you the best golf betting odds to ensure we maximise profits every week.&nbsp;Prices can fluctuate massively in Golf betting so it’s important to have an array of accounts with different bookmakers. This will mean your getting the best odds on our tips every week and could add to thousands of pounds over the course of the year.</p><p>Head over to our <a href="http://stagingonline.net/projects/freesupertips/free-bets/">Golf free bets</a> page where new and current members can get even better value with exclusive offers from our betting partners.</p><h2>Follow Us On Twitter</h2><p>For up to the minute information on a range of golf betting and sports bet opportunities – and a liberal sprinkle of sporting humour – check us out <a href="https://twitter.com/FootySuperTips" target="_blank" rel="no follow noopener noreferrer">@FootySuperTips</a>.</p></div>', 'Golf Tips', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'golf-tips', '', '', '2018-01-16 06:46:45', '2018-01-16 06:46:45', '', 0, 'http://localhost/sirtips/?page_id=154', 0, 'page', '', 0),
