(762, 1, '2018-01-05 12:56:32', '2018-01-05 12:56:32', '<div class="ui horizontal divider invis_clss" style="margin-top:1em;"><i class="ui white custom info icon"></i> More Info</div>\r\n<div class="fst segment blog content" id="seocontent"><h1>Free Golf Betting Tips</h1><p>Wondering who to back at the next golf tournament?</p><p>Whether you’re watching the Majors, the Ryder Cup or the PGA tour, our Golf tipsters at Free Super Tips specialise in finding you value in the golf betting market. We crunch the stats and analyse the players&nbsp;to provide you with the best golf betting tips. Our tipsters will also make sure you&nbsp;get&nbsp;the best Golf betting odds available with our predictions. This will squeeze out even more value and help you bash the bookies.</p><p>Best of all, it’s completely free. No subscriptions, no sign up fees. no memberships– none of that nonsense. Just the best golf bets.</p><h2>When Are Your Golf Tips Posted?</h2><p>Our tips for weekly PGA and European Tour events are updated by Tuesday each week. This gives our tipsters enough time to assess course information, form and analyse last weeks rounds. To make sure we get the value for the Majors – The&nbsp;Masters, US Open, The Open Championship and The U.S. PGA Championship our predictions&nbsp;are posted a week in advance.</p><h2>Predictions For All Golf Majors</h2><h3>The US Masters</h3><p>The first major championship of the year is The US Masters hosted in April from Augusta national in Georgia, USA. Check out our <a href="http://www.freesupertips.co.uk/tips/us-masters-betting-tips-predictions/">US Masters betting tips for 2017</a>.</p><h3>US Open</h3><p>The second major championship of the year is hosted from Erin Hills, Wisconsin USA. Our&nbsp;<a href="http://www.freesupertips.co.uk/tips/us-open-betting-tips-predictions/">2017 US Open betting tips</a>&nbsp;will be live early June for the tournament.</p><h3>The Open Championship</h3><p>Royal Birkdale hosts the 146th Open Championship in 