e year.</p><p>Head over to our <a href="http://www.freesupertips.co.uk/free-bets/">Golf free bets</a> page where new and current members can get even better value with exclusive offers from our betting partners.</p><h2>Follow Us On Twitter</h2><p>For up to the minute information on a range of golf betting and sports bet opportunities – and a liberal sprinkle of sporting humour – check us out <a href="https://twitter.com/FootySuperTips" target="_blank" rel="no follow noopener noreferrer">@FootySuperTips</a>.</p></div>', 'Golf Tips', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '154-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-01-05 12:56:32', '2018-01-05 12:56:32', '', 154, 'http://stagingonline.net/projects/freesupertips/154-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
