ategies that are good to use when looking for good accumulator tips. Our&nbsp;favourite is to look for teams who have good home form, teams always have an advantage playing at home and there can be some real value in close&nbsp;games&nbsp;picking the home side at good odds.</p>\r\n<p>Alternatively you can look for good teams playing away from home for better odds, for example Man City to beat Sunderland&nbsp;away from home would be decent odds to stick in your accumulator because more often than not they’ll win comfortably.</p>\r\n<p>The third and final popular strategy is to back a draw accumulator. These can return huge amounts from as little as 3 or 4 games however they can be very hard to predict draws but if you manage to the pay out is worth it. £10 on three draws will roughly return 50/1 which is a very nice pay day.</p>\r\n<h2>Where can I get a win accumulator free bet?</h2>\r\n<p>Our <a href="http://stagingonline.net/projects/freesupertips/free-bets/">free bet section</a> has over £500’s worth of free bets and bonuses for you to back our accumulators risk free.&nbsp; We told you earlier that accumulators are a great way to turn a small amount of money into a large amount so claim your free bets and bonuses now!</p>\r\n<h2>Do you offer any other Football accumulator tips?</h2>\r\n<p>We offer a wide variety of football accumulator tips other than our win accumulator on a daily basis, check out the others below</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #000000;"><a style="color: #000000;" href="http://stagingonline.net/projects/freesupertips/both-teams-to-score-tips/">Both Teams To Score</a></span></li>\r\n<li style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #000000;"><a style="color: #000000;" href="http://stagingonline.net/projects/freesupertips/both-teams-to-score-and-win-accumulator/">Both&nbsp;Teams To Score &amp; Win</a></span></li>\r\n<li style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #000000;"><a style="color: #000000;" href="http://