ave good home form, teams always have an advantage playing at home and there can be some real value in close games picking the home side at good odds.\r\n\r\nAlternatively you can look for good teams playing away from home for better odds, for example Man City to beat Sunderland away from home would be decent odds to stick in your accumulator because more often than not they’ll win comfortably.\r\n\r\nThe third and final popular strategy is to back a draw accumulator. These can return huge amounts from as little as 3 or 4 games however they can be very hard to predict draws but if you manage to the pay out is worth it. £10 on three draws will roughly return 50/1 which is a very nice pay day.\r\n<h2>Where can I get a win accumulator free bet?</h2>\r\nOur <a href="http://stagingonline.net/projects/freesupertips/free-bets/">free bet section</a> has over £500’s worth of free bets and bonuses for you to back our accumulators risk free.  We told you earlier that accumulators are a great way to turn a small amount of money into a large amount so claim your free bets and bonuses now!\r\n<h2>Do you offer any other Football accumulator tips?</h2>\r\nWe offer a wide variety of football accumulator tips other than our win accumulator on a daily basis, check out the others below\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #000000;"><a style="color: #000000;" href="http://stagingonline.net/projects/freesupertips/both-teams-to-score-tips/">Both Teams To Score</a></span></li>\r\n 	<li style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #000000;"><a style="color: #000000;" href="http://stagingonline.net/projects/freesupertips/both-teams-to-score-and-win-accumulator/">Both Teams To Score &amp; Win</a></span></li>\r\n 	<li style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #000000;"><a style="color: #000000;" href="http://stagingonline.net/projects/freesupertips/premier-league-accumulator-betting-tips/">Premier League</a></span></li>\r\n 	<li style="text-align: left;"><span st