nd watch out! Look for the dirty birds to be a better defensive team this year.</p><p>Matty Ice will still have his lethal receiving corps. Julio Jones, Taylor Gabriel, and Mohamed Sanu will be returning. Running back duo Tevin Coleman and Devonta Freeman will be back as well. Atlanta is poised to win the NFC and win Super Bowl 52.&nbsp;Sarkisian isn’t planning on making any substantial changes to the offensive system. He’s actually going to utilize the no huddle and play action pass a little more. That should play to Atlanta’s strengths., so I’ll think they’ll be even better on offense.</p><h3>16/1 – Atlanta Falcons to win Super Bowl 52!</h3><h2><strong><em>Super Bowl 52 Predictions</em></strong></h2><p>I think it will be an epic match up between The Falcons and the Raiders. But after losing last year, Matt Ryan might just want it more. Look for another high scoring Super Bowl, with the Falcons getting their first franchise ring!</p><p>If you want weekly <a href="http://www.freesupertips.co.uk/freetips/nfl-predictions-picks-and-betting-tips/">NFL predictions</a> including accumulators and match previews for every game then head over to our NFL homepage.</p></div><div id="golf-tips"></div></div>', 'Football Accumulator Tips', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '694-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-01-24 07:44:27', '2018-01-24 07:44:27', '', 694, 'http://stagingonline.net/projects/freesupertips/694-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
