(922, 1, '2018-01-28 19:04:09', '2018-01-28 19:04:09', '<p>The idea behind the bankroll builder is to focus on high-quality tips each day. We post single bets to give us the best chance of making long-term profit. To follow the bankroll builder you’ll need patience and discipline but you could be rewarded with making a steady profit on a monthly basis. Bets will be posted by 12pm each day and include the 3-star rating system seen in our match previews.</p><p><strong>Season Results<br> 2016/17 <span style="color: #99cc00;">+£157.76</span></strong><strong><span style="color: #99cc00;"><br> </span></strong><strong>2015/16 </strong><strong><span style="color: #99cc00;">+£376.05</span></strong></p><h2>Bankroll</h2><p>Set yourself a betting bankroll – money that you will only use for gambling. One thing to note is that it’s important to use money you can afford to lose. Please don’t use your rent money. One way to boost your bankroll easily is to sign up for <strong><a href="http://stagingonline.net/projects/freesupertips/free-bets/">free bets and bonuses</a></strong>.</p><h2>Staking Plan</h2><p>Once you have your bankroll, we recommend sticking to a sensible staking system. You can do this by simply dividing your total bankroll into a % and placing the bet according to your system. For example, if you start with a £500 bankroll, then a sensible stake would be £10 (2%) but it’s all relative to how much your total bankroll is and how much you can afford. You can look at recalculating your staking % whenever you like e.g. at the end of each month but remember that the main aim is to lock-in long-term profit.</p><h2>Bets</h2><p>Our focus is on high quality prematch selections so there will only be a handful each day and there will also be days when there are no selections. We will mainly be focusing on bets from Football but we may also, from time-to-time, include bets from American Football, Basketball, Baseball, Ice Hockey and Tennis. Look out for our rating system which rates the bets out of 3 stars.</p><h2>Results</h2><p>Every bet will be recorded and season results will be added at the end of the year with internal monthly reviews also taking place. This is where we will analyse our performance on how the month went and how we can improve next month.</p><p>If you want more <a href="http://stagingonline.net/projects/freesupertips/free-football-betting-tips/">Football&nbsp;tips</a> today then check out our daily accumulators!</p>', 'Bankroll Builders', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '714-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-01-28 19:04:09', '2018-01-28 19:04:09', '', 714, 'http://stagingonline.net/projects/freesupertips/714-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
